  <summary date="2017-10-05T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Universal Charitable Giving Act of 2017 

This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a deduction from gross income (above-the-line deduction) for charitable contributions of individuals who do not elect to itemize deductions for the taxable year. The deduction may not exceed one-third of the standard deduction of the individual.</summary>
